{"address1": "Plot No-IND 5", "address2": "Sector-1 East Kolkata Township", "city": "Kolkata", "zip": "700107", "country": "India", "phone": "91 33 3984 9675", "fax": "91 33 2442 1003", "website": "https://www.ifbagro.in", "industry": "Beverages - Wineries & Distilleries", "industryKey": "beverages-wineries-distilleries", "industryDisp": "Beverages - Wineries & Distilleries", "sector": "Consumer Defensive", "sectorKey": "consumer-defensive", "sectorDisp": "Consumer Defensive", "longBusinessSummary": "IFB Agro Industries Limited manufactures and bottling of alcoholic beverages and processed marine food in India and internationally. It operates in two segments, Spirit, Spirituous Beverages and Allied Products, and Marine Products. The company operates Aquashop that offers seed, feed, aqua health care products, and farm equipment, as well as laboratory services; grain distillery that produces extra neutral alcohol; DDGS plant that produces animal feed supplement under the IFB Newgen DDGS brand; and IML bottling plants. It also provides ready-to-fry products, including fish fingers, breaded fish fillets, spicy fish sticks, kolkata bhetki fries, fish fritters, prawn pops, fish poppers, butterfly shrimps, prawn torpedoes, prawn cheese balls, prawn patties, and prawn money bags, as well as ready-to-cook prawns. In addition, the company offers formulated fish and shrimp feed products under the Nutrafeed brand and fish feed under the NutraShakti brand, as well as feed supplements for cattle and fish under the Nutrisigma brand. Further, it offers water and soil probiotic, noxious gas remover, toxic gas remover, zeolite + probiotic, pond freshener, special combined minerals, gut probiotic, immunity booster, water softener and moult inducer, binder gel, yeast, BKC 80%, iodine, fishpond sanitizer, fish parasite care-feed, cramp care, oxygen booster, and zeolite products under the Nutra-Essentials brand. Additionally, the company provides dry ice pellets and blocks under the PolarIce brand. It exports products to Belgium, France, Germany, Myanmar, Russia, Italy, Thailand, Japan, Vietnam, the United States, Canada, and the Middle East. IFB Agro Industries Limited was incorporated in 1982 and is based in Kolkata, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 417, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Arup Kumar Banerjee", "age": 73, "title": "Executive Vice Chairman", "yearBorn": 1952, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 18000000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Rahul  Choudhary", "age": 68, "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1957, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Debasis  Ghosh", "age": 53, "title": "Chief Executive Officer of IMIL Business", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Santanu  Ghosh", "age": 62, "title": "Chief Executive Officer of Distillery Business", "yearBorn": 1963, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Swapan Kumar Bayen", "age": 69, "title": "President of Projects & Diversification", "yearBorn": 1956, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Soumitra  Chakraborty", "age": 60, "title": "Chief Executive Officer of Marine Business", "yearBorn": 1965, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Siddhartha  Basu", "age": 55, "title": "Head of Commercial & Integration of Marine Division", "yearBorn": 1970, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Goutam  Bhattacharyya", "age": 67, "title": "Vice President of Information Technology", "yearBorn": 1958, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Kuntal  Roy", "age": 37, "title": "Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "yearBorn": 1988, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exerc